Package com.oracle.cloud.spring.storage

Class StorageAutoConfiguration

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.cloud.spring.storage.StorageAutoConfiguration
@ConditionalOnClass({OracleStorageProtocolResolver.class,com.oracle.bmc.objectstorage.ObjectStorageClient.class}) @AutoConfiguration @Import(OracleStorageProtocolResolver.class) @ConditionalOnProperty(name="spring.cloud.oci.storage.enabled", havingValue="true", matchIfMissing=true) public class StorageAutoConfiguration extends Object
Auto-configuration for initializing the OCI Storage component. Depends on CompartmentProviderAutoConfiguration, CredentialsProviderAutoConfiguration and RegionProviderAutoConfiguration for loading the Authentication configuration
